name: Colonel Cracken
Lore: 'Alliance spy and scout. Often flies support missions for General Madine''s commandos.',
Text: 'Deploys -2 aboard Tala 1. Adds 2 to power of anything he pilots. When piloting Tala 1, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. When opponent deploys a spy or scout to same (or related) exterior site, opponent loses 1 Force.',
